DBIx-SQL-Abstract version 0.01
=============================

DBI and SQL::Abstract functions have been joined to this module in 
order to provide a simple database object mapping layer and to 
implement several higher order database functions.


INSTALLATION

To install this module, type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  DBI
  SQL::Abstract

